290
00:14:16,010 --> 00:14:18,370
I need experienced soldiers and a doctor.

291
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:20,030
That's a tempting offer, Joe.

292
00:14:20,100 --> 00:14:21,980
But we got to keep going.

293
00:14:22,180 --> 00:14:23,250
Clock's ticking on our guy.

294
00:14:23,250 --> 00:14:25,040
In fact, I could use your help.

295
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:27,820
