367
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:29,120
The major didn't believe in the word of Jacob.

368
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:30,550
But he will.

369
00:20:30,990 --> 00:20:33,930
All of you will be given another chance to hear his word

370
00:20:34,100 --> 00:20:36,790
and join the Resurrection Church.

371
00:20:37,160 --> 00:20:38,900
What are you doing? Get down from there.

372
00:20:41,140 --> 00:20:42,240
He's got a weapon!

373
00:20:44,600 --> 00:20:47,550
For as the Father raises the dead and gives them life,

374
00:20:47,550 --> 00:20:50,830
so also the Son gives life to whom he will.

375
00:20:58,060 --> 00:20:58,980
He's gonna turn.

376
00:21:00,760 --> 00:21:01,430
Damn it.

377
00:21:34,060 --> 00:21:35,280
Oh God! Luke!

378
00:21:35,280 --> 00:21:37,810
Help me secure these doors! We have to contain this!

379
00:21:57,450 --> 00:22:00,110
Are you sure you didn't go to Catholic school?

380
00:22:02,150 --> 00:22:03,860
Uh-uh. Go away!

381
00:22:07,170 --> 00:22:09,890
Hey! This is a very bad time to bother us.

382
00:22:09,890 --> 00:22:11,130
Oh, terrible time.

383
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:20,610
Who's there?

384
00:22:24,600 --> 00:22:25,690
Zombies?

385
00:22:26,870 --> 00:22:27,960
