386
00:23:28,210 --> 00:23:29,020
Murphy!

387
00:23:30,610 --> 00:23:31,300
Murphy!

388
00:23:31,540 --> 00:23:32,620
Murphy! Come on!

389
00:23:32,670 --> 00:23:33,450
Come on!

390
00:24:02,640 --> 00:24:04,210
Come on! Let's go! Hurry!

391
00:24:08,070 --> 00:24:10,520
I would give my left nut for that z-whacker right now!

392
00:24:13,620 --> 00:24:14,580
Come on, you guys!

393
00:24:14,580 --> 00:24:15,460
Let's go!

394
00:25:01,240 --> 00:25:02,550
Oh, that was a bad one.

395
00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:04,360
Where's Murphy?

396
00:25:04,530 --> 00:25:06,610
The last we saw, he ran out some other door.

397
00:25:06,650 --> 00:25:08,430
We need a leash for that guy.

398
00:25:35,410 --> 00:25:37,770
Someone wedged that door open for the zombies.

399
00:25:39,760 --> 00:25:40,440
What?

400
00:25:52,870 --> 00:25:54,860
We can barely face these guys one at a time.

401
00:25:54,860 --> 00:25:57,650
This outbreak spreads, they'll be coming at us 50 at a time.

402
00:25:57,690 --> 00:25:59,180
What about Murphy and the others?

403
00:25:59,180 --> 00:26:00,720
I don't know. We need weapons.

404
00:26:03,520 --> 00:26:04,200
Joe.

405
00:26:05,670 --> 00:26:06,850
What the hell happened?

406
00:26:06,950 --> 00:26:08,430
Jacob and his cult.

407
00:26:08,940 --> 00:26:11,660
The ones we let back in slit their throats.

408
00:26:11,710 --> 00:26:13,810
Goddamn suicide zombies.

409
00:26:14,440 --> 00:26:15,890
They sabotaged the doors.

410
00:26:15,890 --> 00:26:17,270
Insane bastards.

411
00:26:17,690 --> 00:26:20,560
Everything we've worked for, it's gone. All gone.

412
00:26:22,620 --> 00:26:23,850
We need weapons.

413
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:26,060
The armory's full of Zs. We can't get in there.

414
00:26:26,070 --> 00:26:27,430
Well you got to have some hidden somewhere.

415
00:26:27,430 --> 00:26:29,110
No. They're all in the cage.

416
00:26:29,110 --> 00:26:29,920
All of them?!

417
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:31,690
How are we supposed to defend ourselves?!

418
00:26:31,690 --> 00:26:33,120
I thought we were zombie-proofed!

419
00:26:33,120 --> 00:26:34,090
Hey, Joe.

420
00:26:34,090 --> 00:26:35,500
You got to pull yourself together, man.

421
00:26:35,500 --> 00:26:36,890
There's got to be a way out of here.

422
00:26:36,990 --> 00:26:37,910
Garnett!

423
00:26:39,820 --> 00:26:41,080
Thank God you're okay.

424
00:26:41,080 --> 00:26:42,100
Where's Murphy?

425
00:26:42,150 --> 00:26:44,270
Got separated. Zombies everywhere.

426
00:26:44,270 --> 00:26:45,100
10K?

427
00:26:45,100 --> 00:26:46,540
He's out there somewhere.

428
00:26:46,660 --> 00:26:49,110
If anyone can make it he can.

429
00:26:49,110 --> 00:26:50,620
If only he had his gun.

430
00:26:52,840 --> 00:26:54,040
You have to get to the emergency exit

431
00:26:54,040 --> 00:26:55,340
before we're completely overrun.

432
00:26:55,340 --> 00:26:56,030
Where is it?

433
00:26:56,030 --> 00:26:56,970
Through those doors.

434
00:26:56,970 --> 00:26:58,980
There's a long hallway ending in a reinforced door.

435
00:26:58,980 --> 00:27:00,240
It leads outside the perimeter.

436
00:27:00,250 --> 00:27:01,820
Don't stop till you hit the woods,

437
00:27:01,820 --> 00:27:03,330
then you can double back around to your truck.

438
00:27:03,330 --> 00:27:04,210
What about you?

439
00:27:04,480 --> 00:27:06,600
I've got to stay and try to save as many as I can.

440
00:27:07,850 --> 00:27:08,550
Ready?

441
00:27:08,620 --> 00:27:09,340
Indeed.

442
00:27:09,340 --> 00:27:10,140
All right, let's go!

443
00:27:32,350 --> 00:27:33,200
Die you freakin' Z!

444
00:27:33,210 --> 00:27:35,260
Human! Human. Human.

445
00:27:35,320 --> 00:27:38,270
Sorry. You look like one of them.

446
00:27:38,270 --> 00:27:40,240
You don't look so good yourself, sweetheart.

447
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:41,990
Look, I need some help.

448
00:27:42,570 --> 00:27:45,440
Okay. We'll stick together. Two of us might have a chance.

449
00:27:58,510 --> 00:27:59,950
Why didn't you help?

450
00:28:02,850 --> 00:28:04,330
Why didn't it attack you?

451
00:28:06,610 --> 00:28:07,750
Are you part of this?!

452
00:28:07,750 --> 00:28:09,060
No! No.

453
00:28:15,490 --> 00:28:17,200
Help me! For God's sake!

454
00:28:17,280 --> 00:28:18,960
Don't leave me!

455
00:28:33,430 --> 00:28:37,120
Come, brothers and sisters! It is as I foretold!

456
00:28:37,120 --> 00:28:38,800
Our Second Coming is here!

457
00:28:39,120 --> 00:28:41,580
Behold the Resurrected!

458
00:28:41,770 --> 00:28:44,720
It's time to take what is rightfully ours.

459
00:28:44,940 --> 00:28:47,120
Bring me the Blasphemers alive.

460
00:28:56,850 --> 00:28:58,350
It's jammed! It won't open!

461
00:28:58,360 --> 00:28:59,770
Turn around! Turn around!

462
00:29:00,710 --> 00:29:02,510
Back up! The door's blocked!

463
00:29:02,510 --> 00:29:03,730
Guys, we're not gonna make it.

464
00:29:10,260 --> 00:29:11,430
We have to turn around!

465
00:29:11,430 --> 00:29:12,410
Go back!

466
00:29:12,420 --> 00:29:13,380
Go back!

467
00:29:16,070 --> 00:29:16,760
Come on!

468
00:29:18,140 --> 00:29:20,310
Charlie, I'm scared.

469
00:29:32,660 --> 00:29:34,220
Push those Zs back!

470
00:29:34,220 --> 00:29:35,430
I can't even turn around.

471
00:29:35,430 --> 00:29:36,320
Push!

472
00:29:40,210 --> 00:29:41,550
Addy! Addy! Addy!

473
00:29:48,830 --> 00:29:50,250
Stay with me! Addy! Come here.

474
00:29:50,250 --> 00:29:51,760
Hey, hey. It's okay.

475
00:29:59,980 --> 00:30:01,380
We're not gonna last much longer.

476
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:13,040
10k!

477
00:30:14,100 --> 00:30:15,080
Come on. Come on.

478
00:30:24,300 --> 00:30:25,320
How do we get out of here?

479
00:30:25,320 --> 00:30:26,680
I've been using the roofs to move.

480
00:30:26,680 --> 00:30:28,270
The cult freaks are in the compound. Armed.

481
00:30:28,370 --> 00:30:29,060
Murphy?

482
00:30:29,070 --> 00:30:29,810
Haven't seen him.

483
00:30:29,810 --> 00:30:30,530
We need weapons.

484
00:30:30,540 --> 00:30:31,900
Then we'll find Murphy. Let's go.

485
00:30:34,090 --> 00:30:36,180
Greetings brothers and sisters.

486
00:30:36,180 --> 00:30:38,000
The Resurrection Church welcomes you.

487
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:39,880
Please raise your hands to the heavens

488
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:42,190
or I will resurrect you where you stand.

489
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:47,560
Let them go.

490
00:30:47,890 --> 00:30:49,730
The Resurrected will take care of them.

491
00:30:50,230 --> 00:30:51,760
The rest of you, come with us.

492
00:31:06,720 --> 00:31:09,130
The last of the Resurrected have been secured.

493
00:31:09,930 --> 00:31:11,670
And those who died today have the honor

494
00:31:11,670 --> 00:31:13,500
of entering into grace ahead of us.

495
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:16,100
Blessed is the path before them.

496
00:31:16,100 --> 00:31:18,190
Blessed will their journey be.

497
00:31:18,600 --> 00:31:20,230
Brothers and sisters,

498
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:23,400
I know you have hate in your hearts right now

499
00:31:24,150 --> 00:31:26,980
and do not come willingly to this test of faith.

500
00:31:27,770 --> 00:31:31,450
But today each of you will become part

501
00:31:31,470 --> 00:31:33,850
of the New Resurrection Church.

502
00:31:34,300 --> 00:31:37,830
First however you must choose how you will serve.

503
00:31:38,670 --> 00:31:40,870
You may join the living flock

504
00:31:40,910 --> 00:31:44,030
and spend your days serving the Resurrected.

505
00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:48,350
Or your souls taking the next step on their journey

506
00:31:48,350 --> 00:31:49,730
to eternal life.

507
00:31:50,100 --> 00:31:52,210
The time has come for you to choose.

508
00:31:53,270 --> 00:31:56,200
Join me and walk among the living

509
00:31:56,330 --> 00:31:58,090
or follow this blasphemer

510
00:31:58,190 --> 00:32:00,400
who thought he could oppose the righteous

511
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:02,330
and now walks among the dead.

512
00:32:18,950 --> 00:32:22,180
Now don't feel sorrow for the Major, brothers and sisters.

513
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:25,260
Although we stood against the man he was,

514
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:29,970
we take joy in his choice to join the Resurrected!

515
00:32:29,970 --> 00:32:32,150
Blessed is the path before him!

516
00:32:32,390 --> 00:32:33,620
What choice?

517
00:32:33,830 --> 00:32:36,550
To live with you lunatics or die and become a zombie?

518
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:39,550
I don't know your name, brother.

519
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:42,860
But I welcome you to the Resurrection Church.

520
00:32:42,860 --> 00:32:45,770
With us you will know everlasting joy and peace.

521
00:32:45,850 --> 00:32:47,390
There was peace here.

522
00:32:47,740 --> 00:32:50,710
Joe Williams, the man you killed, gave you peace.

523
00:32:51,530 --> 00:32:54,450
This was a good place. This was a safe place.

524
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:56,040
And it can be again.

525
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:59,500
It's not too late. Put down your weapons.

526
00:32:59,620 --> 00:33:01,760
Let's live the way that people are supposed to.

527
00:33:01,760 --> 00:33:04,370
Helping one another, working together. It's not too late.

528
00:33:04,370 --> 00:33:07,410
Put down your weapons. Let us free. We'll help you.

529
00:33:07,490 --> 00:33:10,830
The Resurrected aren't any closer to God than you and I are.

530
00:33:15,180 --> 00:33:16,550
I envy you, brother.

531
00:33:18,440 --> 00:33:21,480
The time for you to walk among the Resurrected is near.

532
00:33:21,480 --> 00:33:22,210
Charlie.

533
00:33:26,010 --> 00:33:29,480
I'm gonna kill you, you psychotic bastard.

534
00:33:29,870 --> 00:33:31,390
Don't you worry, sister.

535
00:33:32,210 --> 00:33:34,710
You won't be far behind your Charlie.

536
00:33:37,180 --> 00:33:37,920
Shoot him.

537
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:39,260
I can't get a shot.

538
00:33:42,860 --> 00:33:43,910
I need to get on the roof.

539
00:33:43,910 --> 00:33:44,790
You get the truck.

540
00:33:46,450 --> 00:33:48,820
Rejoice as both of you will walk before me

541
00:33:48,820 --> 00:33:51,060
on the road to everlasting life.

542
00:33:52,290 --> 00:33:53,250
Listen, Jacob.

543
00:33:53,620 --> 00:33:55,780
Kill me, resurrect me,

544
00:33:55,780 --> 00:33:57,760
but spare the others.

545
00:33:59,440 --> 00:34:00,830
Don't be afraid, brother.

546
00:34:01,300 --> 00:34:03,390
I send you to a better place.

547
00:34:03,690 --> 00:34:05,940
Blessed is the path before him!

548
00:34:05,960 --> 00:34:08,570
I am the new Resurrection and the life.

549
00:34:08,580 --> 00:34:12,430
Whoever believes in me, though he die, yet shall he live.

550
00:34:12,430 --> 00:34:13,720
Stop!

551
00:34:30,310 --> 00:34:34,240
If you think the Resurrected are one step closer to heaven

552
00:34:34,530 --> 00:34:36,860
then prepare to meet your new god.

553
00:34:41,610 --> 00:34:42,740
Come, brother.

554
00:34:44,180 --> 00:34:46,170
Step away from the Resurrected.

555
00:34:46,170 --> 00:34:47,840
That's no place for a mortal human.

556
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:50,100
Come join our flock. All are welcome.

557
00:34:52,940 --> 00:34:54,540
Join your flock?

558
00:34:58,020 --> 00:35:02,550
I am not one of the Resurrected.

559
00:35:03,050 --> 00:35:04,880
I'm your Messiah.

560
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:08,560
That's blasphemy, brother.

561
00:35:09,270 --> 00:35:11,870
We can all see you're one of the living.

562
00:35:13,470 --> 00:35:15,200
Eight times!

563
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:17,900
